                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Boum ! Boum !"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> et accorde une </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">étincelle explosive</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> au personnage.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Étincelle explosive</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorsque votre personnage affecté utilise une attaque chargée</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> : Dépense 1 dé </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> en moins et DGT +1.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/25/35653081/ce0014e0d25cd397fef22aafb4b411c0_3870446362682069047.png",
                "id": "talent35022",
                "key": "Bombe rebondissante",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Bombe rebondissante"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et crée une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fleur bombardier</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> sur le terrain adverse.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Fleur bombardier</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorsque votre personnage utilise une capacité</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: Inflige 2 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> à votre personnage actif.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/25/35653081/3f2b5db15d922d53d7d4db8261138f17_7714544170454496335.png",
                "id": "talent40686",
                "key": "Fleur bombardier",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fleur bombardier"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Pyro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fonte </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Évaporation </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Surcharge </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2 et bascule de force la cible pour le personnage suivant</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Brûlure </span>: <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +1 et crée une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">flamme brûlante</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> qui inflige des DGT Pyro à la fin de la manche (Utilisable 1 fois, 2 cumuls maximum)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/25/35653081/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5377668919931297717.png",
                "id": "talent43878",
                "key": "DGT Pyro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Pyro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Attaque chargée</span></strong></p><p>Lorsque le total de vos dés élémentaires est un nombre pair, l'attaque normale utilisée est considérée comme une attaque chargée.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisation</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/25/35653081/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5124634922741595626.png",
